quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  35,1,"“Kuyamikidwa konse nkwa Allah (Yekha) Muumbi wa thambo ndi nthaka (popanda chofanizira), amene adachita angelo kukhala atumwi eni mapiko, awiriawiri; atatuatatu; ndi anayianayi. Amaonjezera mkulenga monga momwe afunira, (palibe chimene chingakanike kwa Iye). Ndithu Allah Ngokhoza chilichonse"
  35,2,"“Chifundo chimene Allah angatsekule kwa anthu, palibe amene angachitsekereze. Ndipo chimene angachiletse palibe amene angachipereke kupatula Iye. Ndipo Iye ndi Mwini mphamvu zoposa, Wanzeru zakuya"
  35,3,"“E inu anthu! Kumbukirani chisomo cha Allah chomwe chili pa inu (pomthokoza). Kodi alipo Mlengi wina osati Allah amene angakupatseni rizq kuchokera kumwamba ndi pansi? Palibe wina wopembedzedwa mwachoonadi, koma Iye. Nanga mukutembenuzidwira kuti"
  35,4,“Ndipo ngati angakutsutse ndithu adatsutsidwanso atumiki amene adalipo patsogolo pako. Ndipo zinthu zonse zidzabwezedwa kwa Allah
  35,5,"“E inu anthu! Ndithu lonjezo la Allah ndi loona. Choncho usakunyengeni moyo wa dziko lapansi, ngakhale mdyerekezi uja wamkulu (Iblis), asakunyengeni pa za Allah"
  35,6,“Ndithu satana ndi mdani wanu; choncho mchiteni kukhala mdani. Iye amaliitanira gulu lake kuti likhale gulu la anthu a ku Moto
  35,7,"“Amene sadakhulupirire (Allah ndi Mtumiki Wake), pa iwo padzakhala chilango chaukali; koma amene akhulupirira ndi kumachita zabwino, iwo adzapeza chikhululuko ndi malipiro aakulu"